APIs For Sending request to Server using Postman JSON data-
Send User data in json form like this using these apis- 
(i) Api- POST http://localhost:8081/api/user
(ii)Json data
{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "birthDate": "2000-01-01"
}
